text: Heikki Väisänen (born 7 January 1943) is a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kajaani
